<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 02</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--black);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--cream);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.35);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gray);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 22mm;
      height: 128mm;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 9mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 12mm;
      max-width: 90mm;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: #222;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Since Block */
    .since-box {
      width: 82mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      padding-top: 5.5mm;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .since {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .since-text {
      max-width: 68mm;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Info Table */
    .info-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .info-table th,
    .info-table td {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding: 3.9mm 0;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: middle;
      font-size: 10.4px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .info-table th {
      width: 34mm;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .info-table td {
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* Visual Area */
    .visual-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 30mm;
      margin-top: 9mm;
    }

    .visual {
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.16);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.72);
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .visual.green {
      background: var(--green);
      border: none;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    }

    .visual img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.65);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-green.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Company Overview</div>

          <h1>
            생활 위생지 제조와<br />
            유통을 기반으로 한<br />
            전문 기업
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            태평제지는 1977년 설립 이후 화장지 제조와 유통을 중심으로,
            일상에 필요한 위생 제품을 안정적으로 공급해온 생활 위생지 전문 기업입니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="since-box">
          <div class="since">Since 1977</div>
          <div class="since-text">
            정직한 품질로 고객의 일상 가까이에서 신뢰를 쌓아왔습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <table class="info-table">
          <tr>
            <th>회사명</th>
            <td>태평제지</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>설립일자</th>
            <td>1977년 3월</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>사업분야</th>
            <td>화장지 제조/유통, 청소용품 도소매</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>브랜드</th>
            <td>브론디 blondy</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>대표이사</th>
            <td>이정욱</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>소재지</th>
            <td>경기도 이천시 마장면 마도로 223번길 22</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>홈페이지</th>
            <td>www.blondy.co.kr</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="visual-row">
          <div class="visual">
            IMAGE AREA
            <!-- 이미지 넣을 때 -->
            <!-- <img src="assets/company-image.jpg" alt=""> -->
          </div>

          <div class="visual green">
            BRAND COLOR
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">02</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
